external_knowledge:
- "Stars of this dataset"比喻在给定条件下的杰出人物;
- "Shining brightly"比喻在特定条件下表现优异的人;
- "Constellation"比喻特定群体或类别;
- "Navigated through a multitude of transformations"比喻经历了多次版本和数据变化;
- "Threshold of excellence"比喻数据质量的高标准。;

sql:
SELECT person_name, phone_number
FROM people
WHERE person_id = 0;

SELECT person_id, person_name, gender, dob, email, phone_number
FROM people
WHERE timestamp_inquiry_sent_out > '2022-06-01';

SELECT person_name
FROM people
WHERE income_level_id > (
    SELECT AVG(income_level_id) AS average_income_level
    FROM people
);

